This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques, specifically transfer learning, deep learning, and multi-instance learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves techniques related to general machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and computer vision (cs.CV).
